Tommy_Solomon http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tommy_Solomon 0 Tame Horomona Rehe, also known by the anglicised name Tommy Solomon, (7 May 1884 – 19 March 1933) is believed by most to have been the last Moriori of unmixed ancestry. Moriori were the indigenous people of the Chatham Islands.
